                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mrs. Mary Garrett; I hung these sheets out to dry at nine o'clock this morning; Mr. Huxley knocked at the door - I ran out - he called Stop thief! and I saw Scott collar the prisoner - he brought him back to the door where the sheets lay.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
